'''亞洲生產力組織'''（{{lang-en|'''A'''sian '''P'''roductivity '''O'''rganization}}，缩写'''APO'''）是一个[[亚太地区|亚太地区]]的[[国际组织|国际组织]]，以提高生产力为目的。该组织根据一份1961年签订的[[政府|政府]]间协议设立<ref name="Wiktor1998">{{cite book|last=Wiktor|first=Christian L.|title=Multilateral Treaty Calendar|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=h8GnNQLGDRQC&pg=PA726|accessdate=2016-12-10|date=1998-03-26|publisher=Martinus Nijhoff Publishers|language=en|isbn=90-411-0584-0|pages=726|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513002610/https://books.google.com/books?id=h8GnNQLGDRQC&pg=PA726|dead-url=no}}</ref>，旨在通過生產力的提升促進[[亞太地區|亞太地區]]社會經濟的可持續發展<ref>{{cite web |author1=國際組織司 |title=亞洲生產力組織（APO） |url=http://www.mofa.gov.tw/igo/News_Content.aspx?n=163B8937FBE0F186&sms=53182B822F41930C&s=E7A9D2917B932845 |website=中華民國外交部 |accessdate=2016-12-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161210115017/http://www.mofa.gov.tw/igo/News_Content.aspx?n=163B8937FBE0F186&sms=53182B822F41930C&s=E7A9D2917B932845 |archivedate=2016-12-10 |language=zh-tw |date=2016-04-22 |quote=「亞洲生產力組織」（Asian Productivity Organization, APO）成立於1961年，總部設在日本東京，旨在透過生產力的提升，促進亞太地區社會經濟之永續發展。 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，现有20个成员国家或地区<ref>{{cite web|title=Member Economies|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/economies/|website=亚洲生产力组织|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018190008/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/economies/|archivedate=2016-10-18|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。APO的战略重点有3个，分别是振兴中小企业、促进地区发展提、升创新主导的生产力，以及普及绿色生产力；除此之外，也致力加强各国生产力機構的合作<ref>{{cite web|title=Overview|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/overview/|website=亚洲生产力组织|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019011214/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/overview/|archivedate=2016-10-19|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要任務也包含培养工业、农业和服务业的组织和人才<ref name="HitchensClausen2012">{{cite book|last1=Hitchens|first1=David M.W.N.|last2=Clausen|first2=Jens|last3=Fichter|first3=Klaus|title=International Environmental Management Benchmarks: Best Practice Experiences from America, Japan and Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=slQyBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA244|accessdate=2016-12-10|date=2012-12-06|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|language=en|isbn=978-3-642-58442-8|page=244|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513023949/https://books.google.com/books?id=slQyBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA244|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现任秘书长是2019年9月就任的Dr. AKP Mochtan<ref>{{cite web|title=Secretary-General|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/secretary-general/|website=亚洲生产力组织|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019011203/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/secretary-general/|archivedate=2016-10-19|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 成立 ==
1959年的第1届亚洲生产力圆桌会议上提出了在亚洲建立生产力组织的设想<ref name="SatoShimomura2013">{{cite book|last1=佐藤|first1=仁|last2=下村|first2=恭民|title=The Rise of Development Donors in Asia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=l0R2G6t_DEUC&pg=PA44|accessdate=2016-12-10|date=2013-05-07|publisher=Routledge|language=en|isbn=978-1-136-22169-9|pages=44|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512153542/https://books.google.com/books?id=l0R2G6t_DEUC&pg=PA44|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亚洲生产力组织于1961年5月11日正式成立<ref>{{cite web|title=History|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/history/|website=亚洲生产力组织|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018125847/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/about/history/|archivedate=2016-10-18|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 成员国家或地区 ==
加入APO的国家或地区须为[[联合国亚洲及太平洋经济社会委员会|联合国亚洲及太平洋经济社会委员会]]（ESCAP）的成员<ref>{{cite web|title=PART XVI Final Provisions - THE CONVENTION ON THE ASIAN PRODUCTIVITY ORGANIZATION|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/convention/part-16-final-provisions/|website=亚洲生产力组织|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921062411/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/convention/part-16-final-provisions/|archivedate=2016-09-21|location=马尼拉|language=en|date=1961-04-14|quote=This Convention shall be open for accession by any Asian Government which is a member of the Economic Commission for Asia and the Far East of the United Nations.|dead-url=no}}</ref>，APO成员在相互合作精神下共享提高生产力的知识、信息与最佳实践<ref>{{cite book|author1=Asian Productivity Organization|title=Compendium of Best Practice Case Studies in Asia|date=2004|isbn=92-833-7034-1|url=http://www.apo-tokyo.org/00e-books/IS-01_CompendiumBPN/APO_BPN.pdf|accessdate=2016-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211042718/http://www.apo-tokyo.org/00e-books/IS-01_CompendiumBPN/APO_BPN.pdf|archivedate=2011-12-11|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
